rows.label: qst001901_msg0001
rows.name:
Mo mo... Why Sekaka take on this
silly job...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0002
rows.name:
Doomed. Completely doomed.
It all over.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0003
rows.name:
Taking job from Superbian... It just like
asking to be swindled!

rows.label: qst001901_msg0004
rows.name:
Salvager Sekaka having little crisis right
now...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0005
rows.name:
Sekaka drawn in with promise of
humongous reward...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0006
rows.name:
Took on job without knowing all little
details...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0007
rows.name:
Mushroom-Feast Salvager Sekaka
was very confident in skills... Thought
could salvage anything with ease!

rows.label: qst001901_msg0008
rows.name:
But items this job ask for not all
able to find by salvaging...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0009
rows.name:
Sekaka asked to get things only Driver
can get! Mo!

rows.label: qst001901_msg0010
rows.name:
Have to pay big penalty fee for not
fulfilling terms of contract...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0011
rows.name:
Also Superbian who give job rather
fearsome... Momomo!

rows.label: qst001901_msg0012
rows.name:
Mo... At this rate, Sekaka never finish
contract.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0013
rows.name:
Sekaka have to ditch boat in Cloud Sea
and cash in insurance money to pay
penalty fee.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0014
rows.name:
Thank you, friend!
Sekaka start to see little dot of
light at end of tunnel.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0015
rows.name: Salvaging contract of Sekaka like this...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0016
rows.name:
Must get 14 Energy Aubergines and
5 Border Sapphires from Liberalitan
Archipelago.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0017
rows.name:
Then need to get hold of
20 Angel Engines.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0018
rows.name: Ah... Not to worry, friend.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0019
rows.name:
Already have 18 Angel Engines. Only
need two more.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0020
rows.name:
Need lots of rare things... But friends
not give up, please!
